    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Make sure you have the right tool in a pinch with the ASR Outdoor Multi Function Credit Card Tool 100 Pack! These devices feature 11 in 1 built in functions - a sun compass, 2 position wrench, key chain hole, 4 position wrench, saw, screw wrench, can opener, bottle opener, blade, screwdriver and a ruler for good measure. Their small design will fit neatly in most credit card-sized slots in a wallet or purse. Make sure to grab a few of these to keep in your bag, backpack, vehicle or boat for an emergency!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 11 in 1 Multi-function Credit Card Sized Wallet Tool Silver</h2>\n  <p>Make sure you have the right tool in a pinch with the ASR Outdoor Multi Function Credit Card Tool 1-100 Pack!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>Practical Multi-tool Card - Fits In Most Wallets (1-100 Pack)</li>\n    <li><strong>Material:</strong> Thick Guage Steel</li>\n    <li>Extra Durable Stainless Steel</li>\n    <li>Performs 11 Functions (see picture #2)</li>\n    <li>Comes w/ Lightweight Black Sheath</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/camping_outdoors/Tools/MT908B-DS_11in1_Multitool_SLV_main_100pk.jpg\" alt=\"Make sure you have the right tool in a pinch with the ASR Outdoor Multi Function Credit Card Tool 1-100 Pack\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 11I1CCT-20PK-330</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 158157123797</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Silver</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>These devices feature 11 in 1 built in functions - a sun compass, 2 position wrench, key chain hole, 4 position wrench, saw, screw wrench, can opener, bottle opener, blade, screwdriver and a ruler for good measure. Their small design will fit neatly in most credit card-sized slots in a wallet or purse. Make sure to grab a few of these to keep in your bag, backpack, vehicle or boat for an emergency!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Make sure you have the right tool in a pinch with the ASR Outdoor Multi Function Credit Card Tool 100 Pack! These devices feature 11 in 1 built in functions - a sun compass, 2 position wrench, key chain hole, 4 position wrench, saw, screw wrench, can opener, bottle opener, blade, screwdriver and a ruler for good measure. Their small design will fit neatly in most credit card-sized slots in a wallet or purse. Make sure to grab a few of these to keep in your bag, backpack, vehicle or boat for an emergency!.",
